{{Infobox person | name = Thierry Bizot | image = | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = 12 May 1962 | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | restingplace = | nationality = | residence = | education = | alma mater = | occupation = Television producer, author | title = | term = | predecessor = | successor = | known for = | boards = | salary = | networth = | spouse = Anne Giafferi | children = | parents = | relatives = }} '''Thierry Bizot''' (born 12 May 1962) is a French television producer and Roman Catholic author. He co-produced ''[[Fais pas ci, fais pas ça]]'' with his wife, Anne Giafferi.<ref name="lefigdelarminat">{{cite news|last1=De Larminat|first1=Astrid|title=Thierry Bizot, cathodique pratiquant|url=http://www.lefigaro.fr/livres/2013/06/13/03005-20130613ARTFIG00495-thierry-bizot-cathodique-pratiquant.php|accessdate=May 7, 2017|work=Le Figaro|date=June 13, 2013}}</ref><ref name="lacroixdecouvredieu">{{cite news|last1=Bouvet|first1=Bruno|title=Thierry Bizot découvre Dieu, sa femme en fait un film|url=http://www.la-croix.com/Religion/Spiritualite/Thierry-Bizot-decouvre-Dieu-sa-femme-en-fait-un-film-_NG_-2011-04-27-562909|accessdate=May 7, 2017|work=La Croix|date=February 4, 2011}}</ref>
